Text: Fw Jim Meltons BrotherBill Melton brother of FSU Alumni Association president Jim Melton passed away Saturday December nd in Houston Thought some would be interested in the below information Thanks Terry inform everyone that MrMeltons brother passed away on Saturday His brothers name William E Melton The Funeral will be held at am on Tuesday at Trinity Pine Baptist Church Trinity Texas Funeral arrangements are being made with the Waller Thornton Funeral Home San Jacinto Street Trinity Texas The number there is Any further information will be passed on to you all Thanks Review your goals twice every day in order to be focused on achieving them Les Brown CDTF

Come meet Matt Ayers Asst FSU Recruiting Coordinator Cc o The Houston Area Seminole Club would like you to join us on Wednesday August nd at SRO Westheimer and Gessner at pm to meet the new FSU Assistant Recruiting Coordinator Matt Ayer he replaced Barry Every for this position Matt will give the club a preview on the FSU football season including a video and questionanswer session This is a great opportunity for the members of the club to make a great impression on Matt during his first year at FSUlets show him how much we love our Seminoles I apologize if you have received this message several timesIm having trouble with group email so I want to make sure I dont miss anyone
